1.0.0.name: wordpress/syntaxhighlighterpro
1.0.0.description:
Live demo
SyntaxHighlighterPro is a wordpress plugin which uses the SyntaxHighlighter to highlight code snippets. Major features: * Support up to 24 languages, including Java,C++,C#,Php,JavaScript,Groovy,Ruby,Python,Perl,XML,SQL etc. * Support up to 5 theme styles, that are Default,Django,Eclipse,Emacs,FadeToGrey,Midnight,RDark. You can easily change the theme in plugin settings. * Allow you to choose what languages will support, which is great to avoid unnecessary JavaScript imports. * BBCode support
